parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delaminating screen can cause the UCONNECT system to malfunction, leading to distractions while driving, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The screen appears to be delaminating
with bubbles or cracks forming on the surface. The system may randomly change radio stations
make phone calls
or adjust climate control settings without user input. The screen may also become unresponsive or freeze.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator or voltage regulator can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience a loss of power
with the battery draining quickly. The alternator may not be charging the battery properly
leading to electrical system failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The warping of the engine block and head can cause engine failure, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The engine may experience misfires
with the check engine light illuminating. The vehicle may also produce white smoke from the exhaust.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake lights can increase the risk of accidents, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's braking.
symptoms: The brake lights may remain illuminated even when the brake pedal is not pressed
or may not illuminate at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power or experience other system failures, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience a loss of power
with electrical systems failing to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the touchscreen/infotainment system can cause random and unpredictable changes to the vehicle's settings, including radio stations, navigation, climate control, and phone calls, which can lead to distracted driving and accidents.
symptoms: The screen is delaminating
causing "ghost touches" or random changes to the vehicle's settings
including radio stations
navigation
climate control
and phone calls; the screen is unresponsive or stuck on a particular screen; the vehicle's systems
such as heating and cooling
are malfunctioning; the backup camera is malfunctioning or stuck on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of the headrest can cause a distraction to the driver, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The headrest deployed unexpectedly while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle is unable to shift out of park; the "service shifter" message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the dashboard can cause a visibility issue due to glare, and may also affect the deployment of the front passenger airbag in the event of a collision.
symptoms: The leather dash is delaminating
causing a visibility issue due to glare.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the navigation system can cause the driver to become lost or disoriented, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The navigation system is showing incorrect location information; the compass is malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fuel leak can cause a fire or explosion, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has a fuel leak.
